As for Bush/Kerry- I don't think a lobotomized baboon could have made the mistakes Bush has done without a moment of pause.  Whatever the rights or wrongs- the Iraq policy has failed miserably, due in no small part to horrible mismanagement, misinformation and exaggeration of threat.  Here are just a few dated quotes to illustrate the incompetence on a single issue:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>I don't believe anyone that I know in the administration ever said that Iraq had nuclear weapons [SEE NEXT QUOTE]. <br>
